  81:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** /*
  82:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** @Note: This interface is implemented to operate in zero-copy mode only:
  83:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****         - Rx Buffers will be allocated from LwIP stack Rx memory pool,
  84:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****           then passed to ETH HAL driver.
  85:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****         - Tx Buffers will be allocated from LwIP stack memory heap,
  86:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****           then passed to ETH HAL driver.
  87:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** 
  88:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** @Notes:
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccnmRTtw.s 			page 3


  89:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   1.a. ETH DMA Rx descriptors must be contiguous, the default count is 4,
  90:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        to customize it please redefine ETH_RX_DESC_CNT in ETH GUI (Rx Descriptor Length)
  91:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        so that updated value will be generated in stm32xxxx_hal_conf.h
  92:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   1.b. ETH DMA Tx descriptors must be contiguous, the default count is 4,
  93:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        to customize it please redefine ETH_TX_DESC_CNT in ETH GUI (Tx Descriptor Length)
  94:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        so that updated value will be generated in stm32xxxx_hal_conf.h
  95:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** 
  96:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   2.a. Rx Buffers number must be between ETH_RX_DESC_CNT and 2*ETH_RX_DESC_CNT
  97:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   2.b. Rx Buffers must have the same size: ETH_RX_BUFFER_SIZE, this value must
  98:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        passed to ETH DMA in the init field (heth.Init.RxBuffLen)
  99:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****   2.c  The RX Ruffers addresses and sizes must be properly defined to be aligned
 100:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c ****        to L1-CACHE line size (32 bytes).
 101:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** */
 102:../../CM7/LWIP/Target/ethernetif.c **** 
